{"lastModified":1752593277964,"uri":"c::30234707298::vessel::d5cc23cc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Montenegro\n\nDiscover the beauty of Montenegro’s coastline aboard Nauti Cat, a premium Lagoon 50 catamaran offering a perfect blend of comfort, space, and performance. Based in Kotor Marina, this spacious and well-equipped yacht is available for skippered charters, allowing you to explore the stunning Adriatic Sea with ease. Whether you’re looking for a relaxing getaway or an adventure-filled sailing experience, Nauti Cat provides an unforgettable journey along Montenegro’s breathtaking bays, historic towns, and hidden anchorages.\n\nWith 5 spacious cabins and 4 bathrooms, this Lagoon 50 catamaran in Montenegro is ideal for families, couples, or groups seeking a private and exclusive sailing holiday. The yacht features a bright panoramic salon, a fully equipped galley, and expansive outdoor spaces, including a flybridge and a large aft cockpit, perfect for dining, lounging, and soaking in the views of the Adriatic.\n\nAboard this catamaran in Montenegro, you can enjoy a custom itinerary designed to explore the best of the region. Cruise through the UNESCO-listed Bay of Kotor, visit the lively towns of Budva and Tivat, or drop anchor in the serene waters of the Luštica Peninsula. Whether you prefer swimming in crystal-clear waters, discovering charming seaside villages, or simply unwinding on deck, Nauti Cat guarantees a smooth and stress-free sailing experience with an experienced skipper navigating the way.\n\nA catamaran charter in Montenegro offers the perfect mix of relaxation and adventure, allowing you to experience the Adriatic in complete comfort. Whether planning a week-long sailing holiday or a short escape, Nauti Cat is the perfect yacht to explore Montenegro’s spectacular coast in style.","blueprint":{"name":"NAUTI CAT","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc23cc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4